sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant W as WebGUI
    participant I as OIDC Provider
    participant G as LLM Gateway
    participant P as LLM Provider
    U->>W: Access platform
    W->>I: Redirect to login
    U->>I: Authenticate
    I-->>W: Return token
    U->>W: Submit prompt
    W->>G: Forward prompt
    G->>P: Request completion
    P-->>G: Return response
    G-->>W: Send response
    W-->>U: Display answer
